formdatahistory.js
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

This script saves form data in localStorage not to lost your input
text by browser crash and so on.

* Usage

  <script src="path/to/formdatahistory.js"></script>
  <script>
    var f = new FDH.Form (form, formName);
    f.watch ();
  </script>

... where /form/ is an HTML form element and /formName/ identifies the
kind of form in the origin.

* Demo

See "demo/bookmarklet-source.js" or
<http://let.hatelabo.jp/wakabatan/let/gYC-xJmuk7W6UA>.

